A G R E E D. If it won't cast more intelligently (and I don't doubt they won't give up the cycles to permit it to cast more logically), than at least minimize it's spellset, or alter it's pattern of casting to use higher damage spells first without melee, then lower level spells, and to have a very very high mana regen (firepets can and do run out of mana, then resort to sucky melee)<br>
