You can. +30 MR/FR/CR via 2 summoned Elemental Blankets (pets do not abide by Lore tags). +15 CR/PR via Shard of the Core. Some potential 100+ Raw AC points in equipping pets with summoned Phanotom armor (Plate) and Foci. Of course, sadly, this doesn't improve our pets MUCH, and it assumes that pets gain benefits of stats on worn items (which would make sense, considering gaining the benefit of Muzzle of Mardu's Haste), but the bonus isn't as great as one might like.<br>
<br>
