AoE fear: Valient Companion (though arguments could be made to improve this spell's viability through uncancelable or fixed duration)<br>
<br>
Bad Pathing isn't .. truely as bad as most people make it out to be. Most can be avoided, in my experience. There are issues with pathing breaks that really screw with us, but all told, it's probably somewhere between 70% and 85% usable everywhere.<br>
<br>
