Frankly, I'm all for interclass dependance, and don't mind sacrificing the ability to regain mana faster for a more powerfull offensive spellset. If you want faster mana regen, ask your local enchanter for a buff for donation, or group with them.<br>
<br>
There are Pro's and Con's for every class. If you could have a class that could do it all, what would be the point of having more than that one class?<br>
